EClass

Class Time

  • java.lang.Object
    • EClass.Time

  • public abstract class Time
extends java.lang.Object
    A Time object holds the milliseconds since the beginning of the current day, have methods to convert the current time into a string and return the current seconds of the time, minutes of the time, and hours of the time.
